list.name: WittyPad-12: Witty Content
list.comment:
I promise commits will be more common in the feature, I hope this large, commit-free period is really odd.
Lots of improvements: * Admin system starts working * Admin/Witty List starts working - Witties can be create, view and modify * Admin/Witty Dashboard starts working - Witty overview, settings, other settings * jquery refreshed to 1.7.2
Reported as Bug: * Too many open files exception on OSX when downloading profile images some times (5-10x). Other operating system is not yet tested. Problem caused by ImageIO.read() in the ImageController. * i18n required on some place
